title: [FSX/P3D] RealAirTurbine Duke V2 FSX
description:
This package includes Turbine Duke V2 for FSX/P3Dv2/P3Dv3.

The installer includes the following changes over the original Turbine Duke V2 packages:

- FSX version has been updated to the new P3D v2/P3D v3 version standards.
- Minor fixes to the sound package to eliminate the mild sound phasing problem.
- Minor fixes to the packages to prevent possible problems with the custom XML sound system.

FSX version of the package has been upgraded to the new P3Dv2/P3Dv3 installer standards for you guys by Leopard87.

"thanks to our good old friend leopard87 for providing the files"



enjoy and please seed
